    Class Description
    CircleState

    RectangleState

    This class handles what happens when RectangleState is currently active on tool bar and set as Current state
    SelectState
    public class SelectState which extends State
    This class handles what happens when Select State is currently active on tool bar and set as Current state
    State
    public class State which implements MouseListener
    This class is used as generalization for other states.
    StateManager
    public class StateManager
    This class contains all the possible states, and manages them, by calling the method StateManager.setCurrentState(State)
